# NIFYA Subscription Worker

This document describes the structure of the NIFYA subscription worker service.

## Overview

The [subscription-worker](mdc:subscription-worker/) service manages subscription processing for the NIFYA platform.
Deployed at: https://subscription-worker-415554190254.us-central1.run.app

## Key Functionality

- Processes subscription events (creation, updates, cancellation)
- Manages billing integration with payment providers
- Handles subscription lifecycle management
- Updates user entitlements based on subscription status
- Generates subscription-related notifications

